proposal:
Hello Catgirl Enthusiasts! 🐾

We've been prowling around your project and are impressed by your vision. We believe we can help you scratch the itch of community growth with some purr-fectly tailored B2B tools. 

1. 🔄 DEX (UNI FACTORY)
   A DEX based on Uniswap V2, with your own custom colors, logo, menus, fees, and tokenlist. Best part? It's a revenue share model. You don't pay us, we just share the cream (commission: 0.00% to 20%).

2. 🎰 Lottery
   A blockchain-based lottery where you can earn 0-30% commission. It's like finding a stray cat and discovering it's a Bengal!

3. 🪙 Wallet
   A multicurrency crypto wallet that supports Bitcoin, Ethereum, and tokens. It's like having a cozy cat bed for all your tokens.

4. 🌾 Farming
   ERC20 Staking & Yield Farming. Attract investment by offering rewards. It's like offering catnip to your investors.

5. 🗳 DAO
   Governance and proposals for your crypto token. Stakeholders can create/vote for proposals without spending on gas. It's like a democratic cat council, without the hissing matches.

6. 🌉 CrossChain
   An EVM compatible blockchain bridge. Connect all EVM blockchains like a cat jumping from one rooftop to another.

7. 🚀 IDOFactory - Launchpad
   A launchpad solution for IDO pools and token locking. Use your token for IDO pools or native coins like ETH, BNB for token lockers. It's like launching a cat into space, but with less animal cruelty.

Remember, you're not playing, you're creating. So let's make some magic together! Check out our demos at https://t.me/onoutdemos and let us know if you're interested. 

P.S. All prices are in USD, not cans of tuna (although we're open to negotiation). 🐟
